### Multi-Tenant SaaS API - Audit Logs
### VS Code REST Client / JetBrains HTTP Client compatible

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@contentType = application/json

### Get tokens first by running auth.http login
@accessToken = {{$dotenv %ACCESS_TOKEN}}
@tenantId = {{$dotenv %TENANT_ID}}

### List audit logs (paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/audit?skip=0&take=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}

### List audit logs - page 2
GET {{baseUrl}}/audit?skip=20&take=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}

### Get audit logs for a specific entity
GET {{baseUrl}}/audit/entity?entity=Membership&entityId=replace-with-entity-id
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}

### Get audit logs for a user entity
GET {{baseUrl}}/audit/entity?entity=User&entityId=replace-with-user-id
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}

### Get audit logs for a tenant entity
GET {{baseUrl}}/audit/entity?entity=Tenant&entityId={{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
